Create a new C++ project and set "Project Options->Parameters->Linker" as

-lbgi
-lgdi32
-lcomdlg32
-luuid
-loleaut32
-lole32
and try executing this sample code; then go for the code that you posted above.

#include<graphics.h>

int main( ){
        initwindow( 700 , 700 , "MY First Program");
        circle(200, 200, 150);
        getch();
        return 0;
}
